{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"RTL (右書き)","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/rtl","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary\">MDN Web Docs 用語集</a>\n\n  <ul>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Localization\">Localization</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/ltr\">LTR (左書き)</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/rtl\">RTL (右書き)</a></li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n</ul>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong>RTL</strong> (<strong>Right To Left</strong>, 右書き) は、テキストが右から左へ書かれることを示す <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Locale\">locale</a> プロパティです。</span>例えば、<code>he</code> ロケール (ヘブライ語) は右書きを定義します。アラビア語 (<code>ar</code>) も右書きで書かれる有名な言語です。</p>\n\n<p>RTL とは対照的に、LTR (Left To Right, 左書き) は、英語 (<code>en</code>, <code>en-US</code>, <code>en-GB</code>, など)、スペイン語 (<code>es</code>)、フランス語 (<code>fr</code>) などの他の言語で使用されます。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"RTL (Right To Left, 右書き) は、テキストが右から左へ書かれることを示す locale プロパティです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"RTL (Right to Left)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"rtl","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"RTL（从右到左）","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/rtl","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/rtl/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/rtl","title":"RTL (右書き)"}],"pageTitle":"RTL (右書き) - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}